This paper deals with managing travel demand using mobile phone data and machine learning techniques. It involves optimization methods and traffic counts, which are related to transportation and infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Other likely sub-categories include cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IT (Information Theory), as these sub-categories also deal with data analysis, optimization, and machine learning techniques.
